  <example>
    <statement>
      <p>
        Regard <m>\R^2</m> as a metric space under the uniform metric (see <xref ref="unif_rn">example</xref>).
        Then the boundary of the unit ball in this space is compact.
      </p>
    </statement>
  </example>

